  <h2>About Droneit</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <p> Looking for a quick job as a drone pilot? Looking for a aerial pictures and video feed?</p>
      <p> Our platform connects you to the people you need! </p>
        <h3> How can I find what and who i need? </h3>
        <p> Everyone has different needs and reasons for wanting aerial pictures (real estate, event, etc..). With that in mind, a cutomer's request includes a category, and a pilot's profile includes his skills and a few pictures or videos of previous jobs he or she has done. </p>
